        You are ready for a dream vacation, then join the El MAJICO team for an unforgettable adventure WALKING WITH THE BALLOON WITH HOT AIR TO LUXURY
        Known as the open-air museum of Egypt, Luxor offers experimenters a chance to see the ancient world at its temples, monuments and tombs. But few visitors can see these historic landmarks from the sky. In this unparalleled adventure with the hot air balloon, see Luxor from above, the desert and you can take amazing photos in the morning light as you soar through the sky.
        Only the sky is above us. It's 5 o'clock in the morning, a golden light can be seen on the horizon, beyond the Nile and the Karnak Temple, and the nacelle sways in the air, hanging from a huge hot air balloon, colored in the boldest colors, but carefully directed . none other than the best captain in the world of the hot air balloon business, in the fascinating city on the banks of the Nile, in Luxor! Did you catch your breath? Have you prepared the camera lenses? Just take a step back and you will be invited to one of the most exciting experiences you can try in Egypt: the balloon flight over the Valley of the Kings!
        The trip schedule is as follows:
        You will be picked up from the hotel where you are staying around 23:00 and we will take the route to Luxor. We will arrive around 4:00 at the base where the adventure will begin, the hot air balloon ride and we will admire the sunrise. The sun rises over the Nile, the Valley of the Kings, the Temple of Karnak, the Temple of Hasepsud and the Colossi of Memnon. (drinks are for a fee).        <br><br>
